  <div class="about-section">
    <h1>About This Application</h1>
    <p>A simple and secure budget planner that streamlines personal finance management. Users can easily register and log</p>
<p>in to access unique, practical tools designed to track spending habits. Effortlessly add total income, categorize expenses,</p>
